---
import avatar from '../../public/images/avatar.jpg';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Cousnay Portfolio</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Actor&family=Alata&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="w-full min-h-screen text-slate-50 bg-pattern bg-zinc-800 bg-cover text-base flex justify-center items-center text-center sm:text-left">
		<div class="card w-[35rem] mx-5">
			<header class="mb-8">
				<ul class="font-Alata flex gap-7 justify-center sm:justify-end items-center">
					<li>
						<a class="opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" href="#">Gallery</a>
					</li>
					<!-- <li>
						<a href="#">Blog</a>
					</li> -->
					<li>
						<a class="opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" href="#">GitHub</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a class="opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" href="#">twitter</a>
					</li>
					<!-- <li>
						<a href="#">behance</a>
					</li> -->
				</ul>
			</header>
			<main>
				<section class="user flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-5 mb-8">
					<div class="avatar relative">
						<div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-orange-300 rounded-full blur-md animate-pulse"></div>
						<img class="w-24 h-24 object-cover rounded-full relative" src={avatar} alt="a headshot of disney">
					</div>
					<div class="name font-Alata text-4xl">Disney Constant</div>
				</section>
				<section class="about">
					<p class="font-Actor text-lg leading-loose">As a <span>front-end</span> developer I have a keen interest in building, maintaining and enhancing user experience, I'm also passionate about the possibilities of <span>AI</span> and its impact in various domains. If I am not coding, you will find that I am an avid <span>photographer</span> capturing moment through my lens. I am excited to connect and discuss our shared interest, if you have come this far to visit me.</p>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
